800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Victorious@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Victorious@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Victorious@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>第一批参加 2025 年胜利音乐节的艺术家已经确定，其中<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kings-of-leon">Kings Of Leon</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queens-of-the-stone-age">Queens Of The Stone Age</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/vampire-weekend">Vampire Weekend</a>处于领先地位。请在下面了解更多详细信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/kings-of-leon-can-we-please-have-fun-3753952">莱昂之王如何恢复自信：“我们还没有准备好放弃”</a></strong></li></ul><p>明年的现场音乐活动（英国最大的都市音乐节）将于 8 月 22 日至 24 日期间重返南海海滨。</p><p>随着新的宣布，石器时代女王已被确认为头条新闻，并将在为期三天的活动的第一天（8 月 22 日星期五）登上舞台。今年夏天，他们为庆祝最新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/queens-of-the-stone-age-in-times-new-room-review-3455962">《In Times New Roman》</a>而进行了重要的巡演，而主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/josh-homme">乔什·霍姆 (Josh Homme)</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/queens-of-the-stone-age-cancel-european-shows-due-to-josh-homme-needing-emergency-surgery-3773173">在接受紧急手术后</a>重返舞台后，该节目也随之推出。</p><p>由于音乐节正在顺利进行，《吸血鬼周末》将成为周六（8 月 23 日）的头条新闻。对于<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ezra-koenig">埃兹拉·科尼格 (Ezra Koenig</a> ) 等人来说，这场演出是在他们的新唱片<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/vampire-weekend-only-god-was-above-us-review-3613120">《Only God Was Below Us》</a>发行之后，以及在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/vampire-weekend-add-extra-brixton-academy-show-to-2024-uk-and-ireland-tour-buy-tickets-3749797">英国和爱尔兰</a>进行的大规模巡演之后进行的。</p><p>最后，胜利 2025 年最后一天的第三个也是最后一个头条新闻是 Kings Of Leon。他们将于周日（8 月 24 日）结束音乐节，此前他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kings-of-leon-announce-huge-summer-2025-uk-shows-in-cardiff-and-lytham-3817790">在卡迪夫和莱瑟姆举行了两场大型夏季演出</a>，届时他们将演唱第九张录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kings-of-leon-can-we-please-have-fun-review-3750216">《Can We Please Have Fun》</a>中的曲目。 </p><figure id="attachment_3762820" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3762820" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3762820" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Kings-of-Leon@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Kings of Leon 的 Caleb Followill 将于 2024 年登台表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Kings-of-Leon@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Kings-of-Leon@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Kings-of-Leon@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Kings-of-Leon@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Kings-of-Leon@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Kings-of-Leon@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3762820" class="wp-caption-text"> Kings of Leon 乐队的 Caleb Followill 于 2024 年在舞台上表演。图片来源：JUAN PABLO Pino/AFP via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bloc-party">Bloc Party</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gabrielle">Gabrielle</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/reytons">Reytons</a>将在胜利之夜加入 Ki​​ngs of Leon，而周六的阵容还将包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nelly-furtado">Nelly Furtado</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis">Travis</a> 。</p><p>在 2025 年活动的开幕之夜，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-kiwanuka">迈克尔·基瓦努卡 (Michael Kiwanuka)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/madness">Madness</a>将在他们面前表演，而这三个晚上的 DJ 将由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/melanie-c">Melanie C</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mike-skinner">迈克·斯金纳 (Mike Skinner)</a>担任，下午的特邀嘉宾将由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-charlatans">The Charlatans</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rizzle-kicks">Rizzle Kicks</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/craig-david">Craig</a>担任<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/craig-david">大卫</a>.</p><p>在此公告中确认的其他艺术家包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shed-seven">Shed Seven</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daniel-bedingfield">Daniel Bedingfield</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/reverend-and-the-makers">Reverend and The Makers</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-zutons">The Zutons</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/caity-baser">Caity Baser</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jamie-webster">Jamie Webster</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/everything-everything">Everything Everything</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-mary-wallopers">The Mary Wallopers</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wunderhorse">Wunderhorse</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-ks">The K&#39;s</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/scouting-for-girls">Scouting For Girls</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bradley-simpson">Bradley Simpson</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-waeve">The Waeve</a>等。</p><p> “我们已经为胜利 2025 年预订了迄今为止最重要的一年，全面覆盖了标志性的头条人物和新兴人才。我们始终希望为我们的粉丝提供最大的价值，并努力创造一个真正适合每个人的周末，”Victorious 首席布克安迪·马什 (Andy Marsh) 在一份新声明中说道。</p><p> “胜利的 2025 年一定会给您带来难忘的表演、回忆和千载难逢的体验！我们迫不及待地想再次见到南海海滨的大家！” </p><figure id="attachment_3762996" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3762996" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3762996" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/josh-homme-roberto-riccuti-getty-1.jpg" alt="乔什·霍姆" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/josh-homme-roberto-riccuti-getty-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/josh-homme-roberto-riccuti-getty-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://w